            "value": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Special Action\" aria-label=\"Special Action\">*</span></p><p><em>When you decide to take a risk, you commit fully in pursuit of the greatest reward.</em></p><p>After you use your @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.heroic-paths.Item.ScqSKbkewDAfSizP]{Opportunist} talent, you can reroll the die one additional time. You must use this final result, and if it includes a <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Always Active\" aria-label=\"Always Active\" style=\"color:rgb(173,19,19)\">c</span>, you lose 2 focus.</p>",
